    narr:narration """This hub gathers captured stock phrases and idiolect markers across the aswritten.ai narrative — distinctive turns of speech treated as recognition handles for speakers and positioning. Several encode product/positioning canon: [institutional knowledge at the cursor](narr:StyleObs_StockPhrase_InstitutionalKnowledge), [senior expert bottleneck](narr:StyleObs_StockPhrase_SeniorExpertBottleneck), and the [graph-as-product marketplace term](narr:StyleObs_StockPhrase). Others are rhetorical reframes: the [builder-trap redefinition](narr:StyleObs_BuilderTrap), [optimization-not-prerequisite scope move](narr:StyleObs_OptimizationNotPrereq), and the [substrate metaphor](narr:StyleObs_3) for narrative architecture. A third band is personal idiolect tied to named speakers — [a design collaborator's route-one-in entry point](narr:StyleObs_RouteOneIn), [the customer's chief architect's killer use case](narr:StyleObs_KillerUseCase), [a beta user from outside tech's 'shit deal' teaching shorthand](narr:StyleObs_ShitDealIdiolect), [a founder beta user's 'like' hedging](narr:StyleObs_LikeFiller), and [Scarlet's 'zombie' env-var metaphor](narr:StyleObs_ZombieIdiolect). Technical-boundary idioms appear too: [thin LLM wrappers](narr:StyleObs_ThinWrapperIdiom), [fire-and-forget](narr:StyleObs_FeatureNotBug), [vibe coding](narr:StyleObs_VibeCoding). Conviction-weight markers ([FOUNDATION / settled design decision](narr:StyleObs_SettledDecisionMarker)) and brand-style rules (lowercase 'aswritten', [the 'Herself' sign-off](narr:StyleObs_Signature_1)) round out the span. No dates, no reconciliation.""" ;
